Savannah has been with Cat Rangers for a while now&nbsp;and we&rsquo;re hoping someone special will give this beautiful girl the loving home she deserves. With her striking green eyes and graceful presence, she&rsquo;s a cat who definitely turns heads.

&nbsp;

Savannah enjoys affection&mdash;especially rubbing against your legs and soaking up gentle pets&mdash;but always on her terms. Like many independent felines, she can become overstimulated and may swat to let you know she needs space.

Because of this, Savannah would do best in a calm, adult-only home with someone who understands and respects her boundaries. She&#39;s not a fan of chaos, but she does love having a cozy spot to call her own and a human companion who lets her be herself.

Savannah may not be a cuddly lap cat, but she has so much charm and personality to offer. Please consider giving her the second chance she&rsquo;s been waiting for.

